flowRoot.flowPara: Now we boil for 60 mins (fully open rings 1 and 3), adding hops as required (in hops bags). The heat exchanger MUST be immersed in the liquid for at least the last 15 minutes of the boil (to sterilize it). Do not put a lid on the boil tank (gives bad flavours). We need a rolling boil (it won't boil over with the lid off).
